<i>Having gone through the special</i>
<i>training for the merging technique Fusion,</i>

27
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:25,740
<i>handed down by Goku to Goten and</i>
<i>Trunks in order to defeat Majin Boo,</i>

28
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:30,290
