<i>to the superhuman warrior Gotenks.</i>

29
00:02:30,330 --> 00:02:33,960
<i>Overconfident of himself,</i>
<i>Gotenks took off by himself,</i>

30
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,540
<i>but was all-too-easily defeated by Boo.</i>

31
