I got beaten up all over!

32
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:10,280
W-What?!

33
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,660
Everybody, everybody...

34
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:14,500
Stop!!

35
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:20,880
Now die!!

36
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:27,180
<i>In just one day, Boo's intensive attacks</i>

37
